{"tid":1667897,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【風高物燥】裝修還裝修，火線還火線～","createTime":"2019-10-21T16:53:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T17:26:17.000Z","uid":269761,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4efaa65c8abf1d97629781199f498fbe9a485050","tid":1667897,"uid":269761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:53:12.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">致善良的前線手足們</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n你們都是善良勇武求變的一群，不割𥱊是共識，請聽我講兩句：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1) 條燈桂跌落嚟打倒手足（一定唔係電光火石），搞咁耐切斷條柱，唔該大聲叫人行開啲。雖然唔知佢有無傷，但少一個手足就少一個，唔好咁白痴～</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i4cmnZv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi4cmnZv.jpg&h=361441f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n2) 火舌好容易蔓延，天氣開始乾燥，商店樓上、地鐵入面嘅人隨時被波及，煙都可以焗死人，知道你唔怕坐監，或者影響整場運動，但係死一個或多個無辜嘅人，你&quot;一世都過意唔去&quot; ！總之，裝修還裝修，火線還火線～</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VKW6y6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVKW6y6h.jpg&h=0c768423&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">智慧勇氣同在</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">願榮光歸香港</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有線新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://l.hkott.hk/en-us/l/open-content?cid=8952&amp;ct=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fl.hkott.hk%2Fen-us%2Fl%2Fopen-content%3Fcid%3D8952%26ct%3D1&d=bp2T%2F%2B5c5q8hcpZmRI3qNlR4K0ufT%2FFGu3kbIPb6xA8%3D&h=d2b234ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://l.hkott.hk/en-us/l/open-content?cid=8952&amp;ct=1</a>"},{"pid":"1f40e169ac76a46d4e874133c2cd03ee865c31b0","tid":1667897,"uid":210452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:11:59.000Z","msg":"黃埔間優品360笑到唔知講咩好<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666947\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666947</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"74fe30270bd40de8d185e5f97164baf2fd33c314","tid":1667897,"uid":11919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:25:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9af1a4577aa016d64c99aadc20a647946af2889","tid":1667897,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:26:17.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1VCzpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1VCzpw.jpg&h=7b29ce56&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYt8F4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYt8F4w.jpg&h=eecde813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2D8F34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2D8F34.png&h=cb82275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"}]}